1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 20=

4
00:01:09,799 --> 00:01:13,000
The envoy may enter
and pay his respects.

5
00:01:18,210 --> 00:01:21,840
- Congratulations on Your Majesty's recovery.
- Congratulations on Your Majesty's recovery.

6
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:24,220
- May Your Majesty enjoy endless fortune.
- May Your Majesty enjoy endless fortune.

7
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:27,079
Let all share in the joy.

8
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:29,490
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

9
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:39,760
I recently learned a new tune

10
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:42,040
and wish to perform it
for Your Majesty's enjoyment.

11
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:46,359
Duke Zhen,
your flute skills are exceptional.

12
00:01:46,879 --> 00:01:48,840
It has been a long time
since I last heard them.

13
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:00,079
(Why does this melody
sound so familiar?)

14
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:33,990
- Your Majesty!
- Your Majesty!

15
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,000
(Something's wrong with the music.)

16
00:02:37,110 --> 00:02:38,620
Your Lordship, your status is too noble.

17
00:02:38,639 --> 00:02:39,400
Please allow me to perform
in your place.

18
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:39,960
How dare you!

19
00:02:41,879 --> 00:02:42,960
My hand slipped.

20
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:44,199
I beg your pardon.

21
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,759
You wretched concubine!

22
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:47,800
How dare you break my flute!

23
00:02:48,319 --> 00:02:49,280
Guards!

24
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,680
Your Majesty!

25
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,240
Your Majesty!

26
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,759
His Majesty has passed away!

27
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,080
What?

28
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:10,759
This is bad!

29
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:12,879
Troops have gathered
outside the palace gates.

30
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:14,479
Your Majesty?

31
00:03:14,879 --> 00:03:16,639
Guards! Protect His Majesty!

32
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,280
Duke Zhen,

33
00:03:19,479 --> 00:03:20,960
you brought troops into the palace.

34
00:03:21,039 --> 00:03:22,199
Are you attempting rebellion?

35
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,520
I'm protecting His Majesty.

36
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:26,319
Someone poisoned him.

37
00:03:26,719 --> 00:03:28,479
It must be

38
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,800
this woman.

39
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,719
You're not dead?

40
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:53,240
Of course I'm not.

41
00:03:53,759 --> 00:03:55,280
Every time you see me,

42
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,700
you shout, "Long live Your Majesty".

43
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,719
Surely, I must live a long life.

44
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,520
Did you think

45
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:02,719
a mere flute could kill me?

46
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:06,319
You lowborn brat
are good at putting on an act.

47
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,199
Fine.

48
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:09,919
I'm done playing along with you.

49
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:12,759
My army has already entered the capital.

50
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:15,960
You would be wise to hand over
the imperial seal.

51
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,920
And if I refuse?

52
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:19,800
Don't blame me for showing no mercy.

53
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,519
Guards.

54
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:21,399
Right now.

55
00:04:27,879 --> 00:04:29,040
Have you all lost your minds?

56
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,879
I'm your true master.

57
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,800
Your troops were replaced

58
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,319
by my men long ago.

59
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,319
You colluded with the Prince of Jin.

60
00:04:36,839 --> 00:04:38,199
I've known all along.

61
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:05,839
Your Majesty,

62
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,680
all of Duke Zhen's men have surrendered.

63
00:05:08,079 --> 00:05:10,639
I've ordered a search
throughout the city for Prince Song.

64
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:14,360
I didn't realize Your Majesty had been
watching Prince Song all this time.

65
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,240
What a pity

66
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:18,480
about Your Majesty's birthday banquet.

67
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:21,720
We haven't properly celebrated
your birthday in years.

68
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:22,879
I had hoped

69
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:24,319
to celebrate it for you.

70
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:28,079
Jiang Heng ruined everything.

71
00:05:28,959 --> 00:05:30,120
It's only a birthday.

72
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:30,850
It doesn't matter.

73
00:05:33,279 --> 00:05:34,519
You were too reckless.

74
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:37,199
You almost ruined His Majesty's plan.

75
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,639
Lady Shen broke the flute to save me.

76
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,279
That's a great merit.

77
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,480
As long as Your Majesty is pleased.

78
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:52,240
Lady Shen,

79
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,839
what reward would you like?

80
00:05:59,199 --> 00:06:00,500
Forgive my boldness, Your Majesty.

81
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,439
But I wish to ask for
a blank imperial decree.

82
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,199
You!

83
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,879
You dare!

84
00:06:06,079 --> 00:06:07,480
I swear on my life

85
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:09,660
that I will never use the blank decree
to harm anyone,

86
00:06:09,670 --> 00:06:11,500
nor will I use it
to seek the position of Empress.

87
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,240
I only wish

88
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,560
for a means

89
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:14,920
to protect myself.

90
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:22,279
Very well.

91
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:29,199
I'll grant you
this blank imperial decree.

92
00:06:29,900 --> 00:06:30,879
Thank you, Your Majesty.

93
00:06:30,879 --> 00:06:34,900
♪Moon sets on palace walls,
breeze hits the gates♪

94
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,399
Your Majesty indulges her far too much.

95
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:42,399
I only hope you won't regret it.

96
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,839
I shall take my leave.

97
00:06:45,639 --> 00:06:46,879
I'll see you out.

98
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:48,680
No need.

99
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,040
You may leave.

100
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:57,120
- Yes.
- Yes.

101
00:06:57,120 --> 00:07:00,540
♪Faint rouge hides
the tenderness in the eyes♪

102
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:04,100
♪Every step is treacherous,
regardless of the world♪

103
00:07:04,500 --> 00:07:07,940
♪In the palace, through dawn and dusk,
who keeps a lamp burning♪

104
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:10,500
A new batch of rare treasures
arrived recently.

105
00:07:10,879 --> 00:07:12,680
I've had them delivered to your palace.

106
00:07:13,079 --> 00:07:14,050
Thank you, Your Majesty.

107
00:07:16,079 --> 00:07:17,279
I'm a little tired.

108
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:18,360
I'll take my leave now.

109
00:07:22,439 --> 00:07:24,399
(She doesn't seem very happy.)

110
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,560
(Did I say something wrong?)

111
00:07:28,319 --> 00:07:29,990
(Now that I have
a blank imperial decree,)

112
00:07:30,079 --> 00:07:31,360
(how should I use it?)

113
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:32,560
You've been leading me around.

114
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,639
How much farther is it?

115
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,839
That man looks familiar.

116
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,079
Move. Quickly.

117
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,199
Are you alright?

118
00:07:50,879 --> 00:07:51,680
Lord Jiang.

119
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,040
What are you doing here?

120
00:07:53,090 --> 00:07:55,279
Didn't you say you wouldn't attend
the imperial birthday banquet?

121
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:56,560
Something serious happened
at the banquet.

122
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,500
Of course I had to come.

123
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,300
I was on my way to Imperial Study

124
00:07:59,759 --> 00:08:00,800
when I saw those two

125
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,160
sneaking into the courtyard.

126
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:04,000
Those two were the Jins.

127
00:08:04,010 --> 00:08:05,590
I've sent someone to inform His Majesty.

128
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:06,900
I'll take you back first,

129
00:08:06,910 --> 00:08:08,300
in case you run into the Jins again.

130
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:11,000
Thank you, Lord Jiang.

131
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:15,399
Master,

132
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:16,480
I've brought him here.

133
00:08:17,639 --> 00:08:19,580
The Emperor is searching the whole city
for you.

134
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:21,480
The palace is the safest place.

135
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,240
Stay here for the time being.

136
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,040
Thank you, eunuch.

137
00:08:31,079 --> 00:08:32,679
Shen Zhinian saw his face

138
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:35,080
on our way here.

139
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,759
He can't be left alive.

140
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:38,080
You killed him,

141
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,679
and now I have to smuggle the body out.

142
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:42,679
Kindly give me a warning
before you act next time, Prince of Jin.

143
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:46,120
Eunuch Pan, you should
be more careful yourself.

144
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:47,919
If something happens to me,

145
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,480
you won't escape either.

146
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,000
Handan.

147
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:55,080
What happened, Young Lady?

148
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,350
Lady Shen was attacked by assassins.

149
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,720
Are you alright, Young Lady?

150
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:00,960
Please sit.

151
00:09:02,300 --> 00:09:04,039
Was it the same person
who poisoned before?

152
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:05,799
Does His Majesty know?

153
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:07,200
I've sent someone to inform him.

154
00:09:07,210 --> 00:09:08,650
The palace won't be peaceful tonight.

155
00:09:08,660 --> 00:09:09,900
Make sure the doors and windows
are locked.

156
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:11,300
In case the Jins come after you again.

157
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:12,919
Thank you, Lord Jiang.

158
00:09:13,490 --> 00:09:14,799
Is your foot alright, Young Lady?

159
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:15,799
I'm fine.

160
00:09:15,890 --> 00:09:17,000
I only twisted it a little.

161
00:09:17,010 --> 00:09:17,790
Let me take a look.

162
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,000
Lord Jiang.

163
00:09:21,860 --> 00:09:22,759
That's not appropriate.

164
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:28,840
I meant no offense.

165
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:29,879
My apologies.

166
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,039
It's alright.

167
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,279
It's getting late.

168
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:34,100
You should return to your duties,
Lord Jiang.

169
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,120
I'll take my leave.

170
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:42,559
It's fortunate

171
00:09:42,639 --> 00:09:43,960
you ran into Lord Jiang.

172
00:09:45,279 --> 00:09:46,360
Lord Jiang said

173
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:48,279
he was on his way to the Imperial Study.

174
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,679
Why would he

175
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:52,399
pass through Shanglin Garden?

176
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:57,120
(Jiang Chen is known everywhere
as a refined gentleman.)

177
00:09:57,879 --> 00:09:59,799
(Why would he suddenly try
to touch my foot?)

178
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:05,039
Your Highness,
the man has been settled in.

179
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:06,919
There are many vacant palaces.

180
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:08,440
As long as he doesn't wander around,

181
00:10:08,559 --> 00:10:09,799
he won't be discovered easily.

182
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:10,879
Mm.

183
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,240
What are you doing?

184
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:18,480
Why did you do that?

185
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,919
You found out?

186
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:26,279
You should never leave loose ends.

187
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:27,730
Have you forgotten what I taught you?

188
00:10:27,919 --> 00:10:29,279
You're losing your temper.

189
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:30,840
That's unusual.

190
00:10:31,799 --> 00:10:33,559
Did someone slight you,

191
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:35,399
so you came here to take it out on me?

192
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,679
I'm nothing like you.

193
00:10:39,279 --> 00:10:40,399
So good at pretending.

194
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,720
Sir.

195
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,759
Stop beating him.

196
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,720
Hide him well.

197
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,759
If anyone discovers him...

198
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,960
You're dead.

199
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:04,960
Don't be afraid, Your Highness.

200
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,320
Lord Jiang is your brother.

201
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,360
He'll protect you.

202
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:10,240
Him?

203
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:13,879
He's more ruthless than Father.

204
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,360
No man in this world

205
00:11:16,799 --> 00:11:18,000
can be relied on.

206
00:11:22,759 --> 00:11:23,639
Your Highness,

207
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:24,759
I...

208
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:28,000
I'm not really a man.

209
00:11:29,759 --> 00:11:31,320
You can trust me.

210
00:11:38,519 --> 00:11:39,720
Pan,

211
00:11:40,159 --> 00:11:41,600
let's go get the military seal.

212
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,519
Once I have the seal,

213
00:11:43,860 --> 00:11:45,279
I won't have to fear anyone anymore.

214
00:11:47,519 --> 00:11:49,200
Nangong Xuanyu doesn't love me.

215
00:11:50,519 --> 00:11:52,100
I don't want to love him anymore either.

216
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:55,200
Chen doesn't care about me,

217
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:58,840
so I won't care about him either.

218
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,039
Alright.

219
00:12:01,879 --> 00:12:03,480
I'll follow Your Highness

220
00:12:03,919 --> 00:12:06,039
through fire and water.

221
00:12:17,879 --> 00:12:18,639
Shen Zhinian.

222
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,720
Why is the door locked?

223
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:21,639
Open it.

224
00:12:22,639 --> 00:12:24,240
Aren't you opening the door, Young Lady?

225
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:26,480
Tell him to leave.

226
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:31,260
Your Majesty, Young Lady was frightened
and has already retired for the night.

227
00:12:31,279 --> 00:12:32,080
Open the door.

228
00:12:32,639 --> 00:12:34,279
Young Lady is asleep.

229
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:36,120
Please come again tomorrow.

230
00:12:40,799 --> 00:12:41,519
Alright, then.

231
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,320
I'll come again tomorrow.

232
00:12:43,799 --> 00:12:44,559
Handan,

233
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,279
take good care of her.

234
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,360
One assassin is still at large.

235
00:12:52,799 --> 00:12:54,440
Be careful these next few days.

236
00:12:54,759 --> 00:12:55,720
Understood.

237
00:12:56,679 --> 00:12:57,519
Tell him to leave.

238
00:12:58,159 --> 00:12:59,879
Understood.
I bid farewell to Your Majesty.

239
00:13:04,380 --> 00:13:06,039
Why are the doors shut
in broad daylight?

240
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:09,080
Open up.

241
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,360
His Majesty is here.

242
00:13:15,279 --> 00:13:16,240
There's no one here.

243
00:13:17,759 --> 00:13:19,200
Did they all go out?

244
00:13:21,159 --> 00:13:22,320
Your Majesty.

245
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:28,960
Why are the doors locked during the day?

246
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:30,360
Where is she?

247
00:13:30,799 --> 00:13:32,480
Her Ladyship went out early this morning.

248
00:13:32,799 --> 00:13:33,639
Where did she go?

249
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:36,200
She left at dawn with Handan.

250
00:13:36,399 --> 00:13:38,399
She said she wanted to take a walk.

251
00:13:39,559 --> 00:13:40,600
Where are the guards?

252
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,480
By your order,

253
00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:44,360
the guards watching Tinglan Palace
were withdrawn

254
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:46,039
after the return from Xunlu Pavilion.

255
00:13:47,639 --> 00:13:48,679
Go to Shanglin Garden.

256
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:50,799
The assassin is still out there.

257
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,039
It's not safe.

258
00:13:57,679 --> 00:13:58,720
Lady Shen.

259
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:03,080
Lord Jiang, were you staying
in the palace all night yesterday?

260
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:05,820
Her Highness suffered heart pains
overnight.

261
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,799
I stayed by her side the whole time.

262
00:14:08,559 --> 00:14:09,559
She likes plum blossoms,

263
00:14:09,799 --> 00:14:11,039
so I cut a few branches.

264
00:14:12,279 --> 00:14:14,039
You're a good brother.

265
00:14:17,800 --> 00:14:19,159
Allow me to give one branch to you.

266
00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:21,590
Consider it an apology
for my impropriety last night.

267
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:26,360
Don't take it to heart, Lord Jiang.

268
00:14:26,519 --> 00:14:27,679
What are you doing?

269
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:43,880
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

270
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:50,840
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

271
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:54,840
♪If we don't meet♪

272
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:58,280
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

273
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:05,000
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

274
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:11,800
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

275
00:15:12,160 --> 00:15:18,480
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

276
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:25,680
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

277
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:32,560
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

278
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:38,680
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

279
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:46,200
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

280
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:53,040
♪Wanting to fold my heart
into a paper kite♪

281
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:59,760
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

